CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 30, 1957, pg. 37, reads: "For Needy Families - Smiling Marjorie Jackson and Delores Burney are showing some of the cans of food brought by the many fellows and girls who attended a 'Sock Hop,' sponsored by the YMCA Phalanx Fraternity, NOv. 22. The goods will go into a Thanksgiving basket for a needy family. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Marjorie Jackson and Delores Burney holding cans of donated food during YMCA "sock hop" dance
